data.description: THIS IS IT! View-tiful home inside and out with picturesque vistas surrounding all sides of this 1+ acre property! Inside you will be greeted by sprawling open space to include an extra large great room perfect for entertaining and comfortable enjoyment. Gorgeous kitchen has Corian countertops and beautiful cabinetry. Split bedroom floorplan provides a large primary suite that can accommodate big furniture along with a window framing the commanding mountain views. High soaring ceilings through the living spaces add a special feel of grandeur! Hall bathroom vanity has been recently upgraded. Fenced backyard space is nicely landscaped and includes a large covered patio. Attached two car garage can fit larger vehicles. Plenty of land space to build a workshop and there is no HOA! This home is truly move in ready and is a joy to see! Home starts here!
